Each component is tough enough for trail duty, so you won't have to worry about your system getting swamped. If you prefer to plug in, you'll find an AUX input and a charging USB input. If you want to expand your system later, the GMR-LED features a full set of preamp outputs, along with a handy camera input. This kit includes a custom-designed dash panel that holds the receiver and blends into your Maverick's dash. Dash speakers made for your Maverick The package includes a pair of NP1-116 Nautic marine speakers that are built for off-road and marine use. The durable poly cones withstand moisture and sunlight, as do the 1' titanium dome tweeters. They're really easy to install, too, thanks to the made-for-the-Maverick X3 speaker enclosures included in this kit. They're easy to install and the left speaker panel works with your Maverick's Smart-Lok(tm). Get your power from a 2-channel amp MB Quart's NA2-400.2 amplifier packs a lot of power into a small package that's perfect for powersports applications.
